reviews.text: They're located on the 4th floor of Square 2, right outside NTUC Fairprice. If you follow this review you're likely to not miss it. But if you're walking around trying to find an ATM, you'll probably not end up here, because it's just extremely hard to chance upon this ATM without needing to walk by it.
